fields.name: fy_start
fields.description: Start of applicable fiscal year range

fields.name: fy_end
fields.description: End of applicable fiscal year range

fields.name: NormRetElig_RetDate
fields.description: If plan member's date of retirement is on or after X, then ... (NormRetElig_age/NormRetElig_tenure/NormRetElig_points)

fields.name: NormRetElig_vesting
fields.description: Plan member's tenure must be X years or greater and satisfy (NormRetElig_points/NormRetElig_age) to be eligible for a deferred benefit.

fields.name: NormRetElig_age
fields.description: Plan member's age at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (NormRetElig_tenure/NormRetElig_points) to be eligible for normal retirement.

fields.name: NormRetElig_tenure
fields.description: Plan member's tenure at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (NormRetElig_age/NormRetElig_points) to be eligible for normal retirement.

fields.name: NormRetElig_points
fields.description: Plan member's age plus tenure at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (NormRetElig_age/NormRetElig_tenure) to be eligible for normal retirement.

fields.name: NormRetElig_SSAge
fields.description: Plan member's age at retirement must equal to or greater than the Social Security Full Retirement Age and satisfy (NormRetElig_tenure/NormRetElig_points) to be eligible for normal retirement.
